Dear <%= @profile.personal_details&.first_name || "Jobseeker" %>,

Your Teaching Vacancies profile has been deactivated. Profiles are deactivated when you do not sign in to them for 6 months or longer.

When your profile is active, school and trust hiring staff can view your details and contact you about jobs by email.

To reactivate your profile, [sign in to your Teaching Vacancies account](<%= jobseekers_sign_in_url %>), go to ‘Your profile’ and select ‘Turn on profile’.

If you have followed the above advice and cannot reactivate your profile, contact [teaching.vacancies@education.gov.uk](mailto:teachingvacancies@education.gov.uk) for assistance.

Kind regards,

     Teaching Vacancies